archimate:Capability.name: License Management
archimate:Capability.documentation: Ability to identify, analyze, track, and administer compliance with a certification of competence in a specified subject or area of expertise, awarded by duly recognized third party, as it applies to a legal entity, an inanimate object such as a conveyer or infrastructure, or an individual.
